nger than an hour: thus were they wont to delude themselves [all their lives]!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3464.mp3","surahId":30,"words":[{"id":51905,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَوْمَ","translation":"এবং যেদিন","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51906,"position":2,"arabic":"تَقُومُ","translation":"সংঘটিত হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51907,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّاعَةُ","translation":"ক্বিয়ামাত","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51908,"position":4,"arabic":"يُقْسِمُ","translation":"শপথ করে বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51909,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُجْرِمُونَ","translation":"অপরাধীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51910,"position":6,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51911,"position":7,"arabic":"لَبِثُوا۟","translation":"তারা অবস্থান করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51912,"position":8,"arabic":"غَيْرَ","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51913,"position":9,"arabic":"سَاعَةٍۢ ۚ","translation":"মুহূর্তকাল","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51915,"position":10,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এরূপেই","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51916,"position":11,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51917,"position":12,"arabic":"يُؤْفَكُونَ","translation":"তাদেরকে পথভ্রষ্ট করা হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/030_055_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51918,"position":13,"arabic":"٥٥","translation":"(৫৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":56,"arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُوا۟ ٱلْعِلْمَ وَٱلْإِيمَٰنَ لَقَدْ لَبِثْتُمْ فِى كِتَٰبِ ٱللَّهِ إِلَىٰ يَوْمِ ٱلْبَعْثِ ۖ فَهَٰذَا يَوْمُ ٱلْبَعْثِ وَلَٰكِنَّكُمْ كُنتُمْ لَا تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"But those who [in their lifetime] were endowed with knowledge and faith will say: “Indeed, you have been tardy in [accepting as true] what God has revealed, [and you have waited] until the Day of Resurrection: this, then, is the Day of Resurrection: but you - you were determined not to know it!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3465.mp3","surahId":30,"words":[{"id":52454,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52455,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যাদের (তারা)","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52456,"position":3,"arabic":"أُوتُوا۟","translation":"দেয়া হয়েছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52457,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْعِلْمَ","translation":"জ্ঞান","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52458,"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْإِيمَـٰنَ","translation":"ও ঈমান","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52459,"position":6,"arabic":"لَقَدْ","translation":"\"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52460,"position":7,"arabic":"لَبِثْتُمْ","translation":"অবস্থান করেছিলে তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52461,"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"অনুসারে","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52462,"position":9,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبِ","translation":"লিখন (বিধান)","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52463,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52464,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"পর্যন্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52465,"position":12,"arabic":"يَوْمِ","translation":"দিবস","audioUrl":"wbw/030_056_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52466,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱل